features.name: Emojiful
features.description: Send and receive emoji directly in chat!

features.name: Optifine
features.description:
The current stable version of OptiFine. This mod enables more advanced graphics customization.
Optifine is required for the Dramatic Sky resourcepack but the modpack will work without it.

NOTE: This is rarely causing graphics glitches however they go away shortly.

features.name: ModernUI
features.description:
A small mod that improves font rendering as well as adding a more modern style of menus.
!This feature REQUIRES Java 11 to work!

This option will also install Emojiful as a dependency.
